reviewText: This is one of my favorite DVDs.  It can be streamed now with a Dove subscription, but having the DVD is really nice.  Beautiful scenery, sticks pretty well to scripture and passes through where Paul and his companions traveled.  Scriptural, beautiful and informative.

4 star - HIGHLY RECOMMEND
ACCURATE
INSPIRING
EX PHOTOGRAHY.
A fine Scripture reader into the bargain.

Les Archer/Corpus Christi TX
